Print summary information about a beam.data object

print.beam.data.Rd

Print summary information about a beam.data object

Usage

# S3 method for class 'beam.data'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An object of class "beam.data"

...

Other arguments passed to or from other methods

Value

Messages about the beam.data object
